OL,4,Ccondition say transplants saved both
OL,5,Ctheir lives
OL,7,FA mother and son say they owe their
OL,8,Flives to organ donors after they both
OL,9,Fwere saved by a heart transplant.
OL,11,FCaroline Sofroniou, from Bicester, has
OL,12,Fa very rare genetic heart condition,
OL,13,Fwhich she lost her mum to when she was
OL,14,Fthree.
OL,16,FHer 10-year-old son, also has the
OL,17,Fcondition, but the two of them have
OL,18,Fsurvived following transplants.
