OL,7,FHowever, donor numbers are down,
OL,8,Fdespite the fact that in the UK, those
OL,9,Fover 18 people are automatically
OL,10,Fconsidered for organ donation when
OL,11,Fthey die.
OL,13,FThe gap is thought to partly be down
OL,14,Fto cases involving children, as
OL,15,Fconsent for organ donation still needs
OL,16,Fto be given by families.
