OL,7,FMs Sofroniou is now organising a
OL,8,Fcharity football match in Bicester,
OL,9,Fand a dog show, to raise funds and
OL,10,Fawareness of how heart donation and
OL,11,Ftruly transform lives.
OL,13,FGenerations of Caroline's family
OL,14,Finherited the rare genetic heart
OL,15,Fconditions, Hypertrophic
OL,16,FCardiomyopathy alongside Danon's
OL,17,Fdisease.
