OL,3,CMother and son with rare heart
OL,4,Ccondition say transplants saved both
OL,5,Ctheir lives
OL,7,FCaroline Sofroniou said: "The heart
OL,8,Fmuscle gets thick and as it gets
OL,9,Fthicker, it's really difficult to
OL,10,Fwalk, or even hold a conversation.
OL,12,F"For myself it was scary, but with
OL,13,FJayden having his transplant, it was
OL,14,Fabove how scary it was for me, but we
OL,15,Fknew he'd come through, we knew how
OL,16,Fmuch of a warrior he was."
OL,18,FHer son Jayden had three false alarms
OL,19,Fbefore he finally found the right
OL,20,Fmatch for the transplant that has
OL,21,Fchanged his life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
