OL,4,Ccondition say transplants saved both
OL,5,Ctheir lives
OL,7,FWhen Jayden was asked what the best
OL,8,Fbit is about his life now he's had the
OL,9,Ftransplant, he said, "living... and
OL,10,Fhorse riding."
OL,12,FIn the UK, more than 7,000 are still
OL,13,Fwaiting for a transplant, 91 people
OL,14,Fare on the list in Oxfordshire, in
OL,15,FBerkshire it is 108, and in Hampshire
OL,16,Fit is 202.
OL,18,FLucy Dames, Organ donation nurse said:
OL,19,F"There's a real gap between organ
OL,20,Fdonors and the number of people that
OL,21,Fneed a transplant.
